Mountain Bike Analytics

We use data to answer interesting questions from bike set up (e.g., what tire pressure should I run?) to the World Cup Downhill performance (e.g., who has the highest raw speed?). All our methods, data, and code are open-source. Currently partnering with VitalMTB.
